text: Erika Christensen (born August 19, 1982) is an American actress who has acted in many movies and television programs. She played Julia on the NBC family series Parenthood. She also played Caroline in the movie Traffic. She was born in Seattle, Washington. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Seattle Category:1982 births Category:Living people
